name: Rebel Trooper (V)
Lore: 'Corellian Corvette trooper Ensign Chad Hilse, an Alderaanian, typifies the loyal Rebel volunteers dedicated to defeating the Empire. Trained in starship and ground combat.',
Text: 'When drawn for weapon or battle destiny, destiny +2. While present at a site and armed with a blaster rifle, forfeit +2 and draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.',
